<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Data Deletion Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #044B52;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Request to Delete Your Data</h1>
    <p>If you wish to delete your personal data from the Laudamus app, please follow the steps below:</p>
    
    <h2>Steps to Delete Your Data</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Open the <strong>Laudamus</strong> app on your device.</li>
        <li>Go to the <strong>Settings</strong> section.</li>
        <li>Select <strong>Manage Account</strong>.</li>
        <li>Select <strong>Delete My Account</strong>.</li>
        <li>Confirm the deletion request by Authenticating.</li>
    </ol>
    
    <p>Once the deletion is confirmed, all your personal data will be permanently removed from our system.</p>
    
    <h2>Need Help?</h2>
    <p>If you have any issues or need assistance, contact our support team through the app.</p>

    <p><a href="https://ddiasguto.github.io/laudamus-privacy/">Back to Privacy Policy</a></p>
</body>
</html>
